{"tid":264333,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真]大家支唔支持漁翁撒網?","createTime":"2017-05-30T17:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T07:33:59.000Z","uid":55641,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce53c419818e49fbef306600de57954908623bef","tid":264333,"uid":55641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:15:58.000Z","msg":"識得有人透過唔同渠道不斷咁識異性(1個月十幾個)<br />\n見佢覆message都覆唔切 個個都排住隊等佢覆<br />\n岩傾就繼續, 唔岩就即block, 務求搵到可發展對象<br />\n到底咁樣係咪真係work?<br />\n如果你傾開個個人同時同n條友message緊, 你又會點睇?<br />\n<br />\n認真討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位巴打絲打點睇"},{"pid":"4713cf6c2875420c822e50ad564cc79dbb43d64c","tid":264333,"uid":80226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:18:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得係未搵到真正岩的人之前，漁翁撒網未嘗不可，但真係拍拖，佢肯認真專一咪得。不過一個月十幾個又真係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f791474c21d2406b568ba859bbe63ab6bc72d6","tid":264333,"uid":78026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得係未搵到真正岩的人之前，漁翁撒網未嘗不可，但真係拍拖，佢肯認真專一咪得。不過一個月十幾個又真係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n思想一致 做個朋友啦我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380a25085cea17bfa456c50508d9e5df88ac6a6a","tid":264333,"uid":3935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T20:48:31.000Z","msg":"好出奇咩, 我條仔兩年前日日見三條女添啦<br />\n不過佢都係一厭左就唔覆人果d<br />\n結果都斷晒聯絡靜左一排<br />\n然後一年前識我就比我溝左<br />\n<br />\n不過講真條仔曾經不停識女係唔係個個人都過到自己"},{"pid":"cb2c10d840f361f5969ef6d50378da21d3fb2b06","tid":264333,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T21:55:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80c17db05957142212eab4ad9449ff6b6320d637","tid":264333,"uid":44509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:19:42.000Z","msg":"講得好聽咪漁翁撒網囉，難聽啲咪係狗公囉"},{"pid":"adc4c84546707e522e1d731946084666083040bb","tid":264333,"uid":40461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:30:20.000Z","msg":"基本上支持，但漁翁撒網有樣唔好，就係太多選擇，而且太容易有新朋友，你會好挑剔會揀唔到"},{"pid":"861b78725cdf95fb78e95fad950f1398e8f29efc","tid":264333,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:32:54.000Z","msg":"呢d叫為拍拖而拍拖<br />\n求其執件都拍得咁你鍾意條女極有限啦"},{"pid":"794134486452b717ccb32aed6d3b4fc658e42547","tid":264333,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:00:35.000Z","msg":"點解一個月可以識到十幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我十幾年都識唔到一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02709b8a161c7e5781fc1b4512a664a6938ae550","tid":264333,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:12:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e283d8b285aa218606895f7631aceb0bf6c0e170","tid":264333,"uid":40461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解一個月可以識到十幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我十幾年都識唔到一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要識有幾難？一星期識十幾個都得啦<br />\n要做到朋友，深入了解先難"}]}